('200104003015','(a)$$\\overrightarrow{PQ} = \\overrightarrow{OQ} - \\overrightarrow{OP}$$;$$ = (9i - 7j - 2k) - (3i - j + k)$$;$$ = 6i - 6j -3k$$;$$\\therefore PQ \\equiv | \\overrightarrow{PQ} | = \\sqrt{6^2 + 6^2 + 3^2} = 9$$ units (ans);;Unit vector in the direction of $$\\overrightarrow{PQ}$$.;$$ = \\frac{\\overrightarrow{PQ}}{|\\overrightarrow{PQ}|} = \\frac{1}{9}(6i - 6j -3k)$$;$$ = \\frac{2}{3}i - \\frac{2}{3}j - \\frac{1}{3}k$$ (ans);;Line $$l$$ : $$\\frac{x - 3}{ - 2} = \\frac{y + 1}{1} = \\frac{z - 1}{2}$$;$$\\equiv (3i - j + k) + t( - 2i + j + 2k)$$, $$t \\in \\mathbb{R}$$;Let $$m$$ = direction vector of $$l = - 2i + j + 2k$$;;(i) Length of the projection of $$PQ$$ onto $$l$$,;$$p = \\frac{|\\overrightarrow{PQ}.m|}{|m|} = \\frac{(6i - 6j -3k).(- 2i + j + 2k)}{|- 2i + j + 2k|}$$;$$ = \\frac{| -12 - 6 - 6|}{\\sqrt{2^2 + 1^2 + 2^2}} = 8$$ units (ans);;(ii) $$P$$ is on $$l$$;$$\\Rightarrow$$ Length of perpendicular from $$Q$$ to $$l$$,;$$d = \\sqrt{PQ^2 - p^2}$$;$$ = \\sqrt{9^2 - 8^2}$$;$$ = \\sqrt{17}$$ units (ans);;(b)$$(b - c) \\cdot (b - c) = (b - c)\\cdot b - (b - c)\\cdot c$$;$$ = b.b - c.b - b.c + c.c$$;$$ = {| b |}^2 + {| c |}^2 - 2b.c$$ (ans);;$$b = \\overrightarrow{AC}$$ and  $$c = \\overrightarrow{AB}   \\Rightarrow b - c = \\overrightarrow{BC}$$;$$ {| b |}^2 + {| c |}^2 - (b - c) \\cdot (b - c) = 2 b \\cdot c$$;$$\\equiv {| b |}^2 + {| c |}^2 - {| b - c |}^2 = 2 | b | | c | \\cos \\angle BAC$$;$$\\equiv AC^2 + AB^2 - BC^2 = 2.AC.AB.\\cos \\angle BAC$$;$$\\equiv BC^2 = AC^2 + AB^2 - 2.AC.AB.\\cos \\angle BAC$$;--- the cosine formula for triangle ABC.'),
